V6.0c - [04/12/2011]
* started working on locales for ingame config. will need help in other languages when complete!
* fixed power bar for onyxia/nef fight
* tweaked placement of boss frames again....
* filger is no longer included as i elected to go back to classtimers style of tracking like i did in my wraith edit! (filger still functions you will need to disable classtimers in config though)

V6.0b - [04/11/2011]
* /bags command no longer neccessary, all commadns built into bags now (purchase, sort)
* added option to configure raid buffs (dps and healer layouts) ingame through filters config section
* added some procs/buffs for deathknights in filger config section
* fixed tags for dps layouts
* added option to hideshapeshift unless mousedover

V6.0 - [04/10/2011]
* updated stat block code condensed one block, and moved markbar to spawn there instead
* updated latency code to show bandwidth usage when patch 4.1 goes live
* can now customize spell filters, error msgs, and other filters ingame
* fixed some bugs with buffs on player/target/tot/focus frames, and tweaked them in the process....
* adjusted boss frames layout slightly, and moved them up a bit to acct for tooltips if shown in combat
* temp hack/fix with tooltip border colors if unitframes are disabled
* fixed bug causing lua errors if battle.net was down
* removed pet happiness notifications as its no longer used come patch 4.1
* added NEW datatext to display mana regeneration
* added option to hide location panel while in combat
* adjusted text in boss frames slightly
* moved up castbars when outside of unitframes
* adjust positions of: filger icons to not have so much overlapping
* adjusted placement of xct text. most overlapping should be gone.. give or take a few. report them in forums if found!
* added skinning for skada

